    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Methodology of solving problems in statics by analysis using graphic methods such as diagrams, rather than pure mathematical and other calculations; for example, using a scale drawing of the associated forces and reactions in order to estimate effects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
